Yeah. Drawers opened, tossed through.

58
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:08,860
床垫被翻过来了，很可能是抢劫
Mattress flipped. Probably robbery.

59
00:12:09,030 --> 00:12:10,500
或者是制造抢劫假象
Or made to look like one.

60
00:12:10,670 --> 00:12:12,430
看见了吗
See this?

61
00:12:12,740 --> 00:12:15,970
与总统握手
-Shaking hands with the president.
FlNE: Whoa.

62
00:12:16,140 --> 00:12:18,370
你觉得布莱克是间谍吗
Think Blake was a spook?

63
00:12:18,540 --> 00:12:22,210
政府间谍还是秘密间谍？
Government or black ops?

64
00:12:22,510 --> 00:12:24,410
我觉得…
GALLAGHER:
I think...

65
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:28,010
这件事不是你我能处理得了的
...this is way bigger than both of us.

66
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:36,420
罗夏日记，1985年10月12日
RORSCHACH:
Rorschach's journal, October 12th, 1985.

67
00:12:36,590 --> 00:12:41,690
早上小巷里出现狗的尸体，被轮胎碾过
Dog carcass in alley this morning.
Tire tread on burst stomach.

68
00:12:41,970 --> 00:12:44,200
这个城市害怕我
This city's afraid of me.

69
00:12:44,370 --> 00:12:48,300
我见过它的真实面孔，街道只是另一种排水沟
I've seen its true face.
The streets are extended gutters...

70
00:12:48,970 --> 00:12:51,370
而排水沟里流的是血
...and the gutters are full of blood.

71
00:12:51,540 --> 00:12:54,010
当排水沟最终毁掉的时候
And when the drains finally scab over...

72
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:57,310
所有的歹人都会淹死
...all the vermin will drown.

73
00:12:57,950 --> 00:13:00,350
他们的性和谋杀积累起来的罪行
The accumulated filth of all their sex
and murder...

74
00:13:00,520 --> 00:13:02,820
会把他们淹没
... will foam up around their waists...

75
00:13:02,990 --> 00:13:08,450
所有的娼妓和政客会大喊，“救命”
...and all the whores and politicians
will look up and shout, "Save us. "

76
00:13:09,430 --> 00:13:13,060
我会轻轻地说，“不”
And I'll whisper, "No. "

77
00:13:14,570 --> 00:13:17,430
现在整个世界正站在悬崖边上
Now the whole world
stands on the brink...

78
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:20,090
看着悬崖下的末日
...staring down into bloody hell.

79
00:13:20,270 --> 00:13:23,800
所有的自由主义者，知识分子
All those liberals and intellectuals...

80
00:13:23,970 --> 00:13:25,970
和能说会道的政客
...and smooth talkers...

81
00:13:26,140 --> 00:13:29,600
都突然不知道该说什么
...and all of a sudden,
nobody can think of anything to say.

82
00:13:29,780 --> 00:13:32,940
我下面的城市
Beneath me, this awful city.

83
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:36,880
就像充满尖叫的智障儿童的屠宰场
It screams like an abattoir
full of retarded children...

84
00:13:37,050 --> 00:13:41,680
在夜晚到处都是奸情与罪恶
...and the night reeks of fornication
and bad consciences.

85
00:15:02,270 --> 00:15:06,400
