Truth?

114
00:17:38,200 --> 00:17:41,930
你是个比我还要出色的猫头鹰，丹尼尔
You were a better Nite Owl
than I ever was, Danny boy.

115
00:17:42,100 --> 00:17:45,830
霍利斯，这句话分明是胡说
-Hollis, we both know that's bullshit.
-Hey.

116
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:47,270
