When he' s dead.

127
00:18:13,760 --> 00:18:15,860
-下周？-呃…
DAN: Next week?
HOLLlS: Well...

128
00:18:16,030 --> 00:18:20,630
你不用总是这么迁就我
...you know, you don't have to
keep humoring me like this.

129
