如果你和漂亮女人有约会…
If you got a hot date or something....

130
00:18:23,140 --> 00:18:25,940
嘿，我们退休的猫头鹰应该团结在一起
Hey, us retired guys
have to stick together, right?

131
00:18:27,710 --> 00:18:29,580
怀念以前的生活吗
You ever miss it?

132
00:18:30,780 --> 00:18:32,870
不，你呢
No. You?

133
00:18:33,450 --> 00:18:35,250
一点也不
Oh, heck, no.

134
00:18:36,550 --> 00:18:38,320
再见
Be seeing you.

135
00:19:52,100 --> 00:19:53,390
你好，丹尼尔
Hello, Daniel.

136
00:19:54,130 --> 00:19:55,220
罗夏
Rorschach.

137
00:19:56,300 --> 00:20:00,600
我自己找了些豆子吃，希望你不介意
Helped myself to some beans.
Hope you don't mind.

138
00:20:00,770 --> 00:20:03,210
当然不介意
No, no. Course not.

139
00:20:04,810 --> 00:20:07,370
要不要加热一下
You want me to heat those up for you?

140
00:20:07,540 --> 00:20:09,070
这样就很好
Fine like this.

141
00:20:10,650 --> 00:20:11,840
你近来怎么样
How have you been keeping?

142
00:20:16,220 --> 00:20:18,020
出狱了
RORSCHACH:
Out of prison.

143
00:20:19,720 --> 00:20:21,950
目前是
Heard about you on the news.

144
00:20:22,560 --> 00:20:24,790
听说你袭击了警察
Say you attacked a cop.

145
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:27,730
轻伤，都不需要住院
RORSCHACH: Minor wound.
Won't need hospitalization.

146
00:20:28,600 --> 00:20:29,760
丹尼尔
Daniel...

147
00:20:29,930 --> 00:20:31,230
看
...Iook at this.

148
