It could have been a burglary.

152
00:20:59,160 --> 00:21:01,860
也许凶手根本不认识喜剧演员
Maybe the killer didn't know
who the Comedian was.

153
00:21:02,030 --> 00:21:06,770
普通破门盗窃案？能杀了喜剧演员？太荒唐了
RORSCHACH: An ordinary burglar?
Kill the Comedian? Ridiculous.

154
00:21:08,340 --> 00:21:11,770
我听说自从1977年他就为政府工作
I heard he'd been working
for the government since '77...

155
00:21:11,940 --> 00:21:15,110
颠覆南美洲的共产主义国家
...knocking over Marxist republics
in South America.

156
00:21:15,280 --> 00:21:18,210
