好的,弄好了
Yeah. There you go.

1262
01:53:03,450 --> 01:53:06,080
丹,怎么了？
Dan, what's wrong?

1263
01:53:07,760 --> 01:53:08,880
抱歉,我
Sorry, l....

1264
