how long now, Lloyd?

1276
01:54:06,550 --> 01:54:08,680
大概15年了
LLOYD:
Almost 1 5 years, Mr. Figure.

1277
01:54:09,020 --> 01:54:10,350
没错
That's right.

1278
01:54:11,350 --> 01:54:14,850
