I'm gonna tear this guy a new hole.

1287
01:54:47,890 --> 01:54:50,880
别激动,劳伦斯,快了
Relax, Lawrence. Soon.

1288
01:54:51,730 --> 01:54:53,060
走吧
Come on.

1289
01:56:21,580 --> 01:56:22,910
丹？
Dan?

1290
