Let's go.

1305
01:58:24,970 --> 01:58:27,340
我能看见,好的,抓紧了
LAURlE: I can see it.
DAN: All right, hold on.

1306
01:58:38,190 --> 01:58:39,620
丹,这里面还有孩子
LAURlE:
Dan, there are kids in there.

1307
01:58:39,790 --> 01:58:41,950
