Everyone, stay where you are
and remain calm.

1308
01:58:42,120 --> 01:58:44,320
我们会救你们出来的
We're gonna get you out of there.

1309
01:58:44,490 --> 01:58:46,650
房顶要塌了,送我过去
The roof's starting to cave.
Get me in there.

1310
01:58:46,830 --> 01:58:48,300
我送你过去
DAN:
I'm gonna get you close.

1311
01:59:47,060 --> 01:59:48,420
走吧
Let's go.

1312
01:59:48,590 --> 01:59:49,750
快
Come on.

1313
01:59:49,930 --> 01:59:51,520
大家快点
All right, let's move it, people.

1314
01:59:58,270 --> 02:00:03,070
妈妈,在宇宙火箭里的那个人
Mom, is that guy in the space rocket...?

1315
