1379
02:10:44,650 --> 02:10:46,770
你没事吧？
Are you all right?

1380
02:10:48,220 --> 02:10:50,410
没,只是…
Yeah. Just...

1381
02:10:50,850 --> 02:10:52,110
有点沉重,你知道吧？
...heavy, you know?

1382
02:10:52,920 --> 02:10:55,010
战争,越狱
War, jailbreak.

1383
02:10:55,560 --> 02:11:00,430
别担心,一切会好起来的
Don't worry about it. Okay?
Everything's gonna be fine.

1384
02:11:05,430 --> 02:11:08,460
你好,劳丽
乔
-Hello, Laurie.
-Jon.

1385
02:11:08,640 --> 02:11:12,270
