你已经知道结尾,为什么还要辩解呢
Why even argue about it
if you already know how this is gonna end?

1504
02:20:11,180 --> 02:20:13,440
我没有别的选择
I have no choice.

1505
02:20:14,750 --> 02:20:17,680
一切都是注定的
Everything is preordained.

1506
02:20:17,850 --> 02:20:20,180
包括我的反应
Even my responses.

1507
02:20:21,160 --> 02:20:24,750
你要经历那些动作
And you're just going through
the motions.

1508
02:20:24,930 --> 02:20:28,330
宇宙中最强大的东西仍然只是一个木偶
The most powerful thing in the universe
is still just a puppet.

1509
02:20:31,470 --> 02:20:34,130
我们都是木偶,劳丽
We are all puppets, Laurie.

1510
02:20:35,070 --> 02:20:37,560
我只不过是能看见绳子的木偶
I'm just a puppet
who can see the strings.

1511
02:20:37,740 --> 02:20:39,430
如果你错了呢
And what if you're wrong?

1512
02:20:39,610 --> 02:20:44,100
为什么我对时间的看法这么困扰你
Why does my perception of time
distress you so?

1513
02:20:44,280 --> 02:20:46,180
因为这是没有人性的
Because it's inhuman.

1514
02:20:46,350 --> 02:20:48,750
因为这让我疯狂
Because it makes me insane.

1515
02:20:48,920 --> 02:20:52,820
你经常说你想安慰我,但并不管用
You always say you wanna comfort me.
Well, it isn't working.

1516
02:21:00,230 --> 02:21:02,720
听着,我不想争吵
Look, I don't wanna fight.

1517
02:21:04,230 --> 02:21:06,960
很抱歉我和丹尼睡觉了
I'm sorry I slept with Dan.

1518
02:21:07,530 --> 02:21:09,560
你和丹尼睡觉了？
You slept with Dan?

1519
02:21:11,270 --> 02:21:14,260
你刚才说过你已经知道了
You just said that you already
knew about that.

1520
02:21:14,980 --> 02:21:18,970
我经常说
I said often...

1521
02:21:19,650 --> 02:21:23,980
你是我和人类连接的唯一纽带
...that you were my only
remaining link to humanity.

1522
