1524
02:21:32,330 --> 02:21:34,390
那就全当是为我吧
Then do it for me.

1525
02:21:35,260 --> 02:21:36,660
如果你真的在乎的话
If you really care.

1526
02:21:36,830 --> 02:21:40,270
你离开我的那一天,我就离开了地球
When you left me, I left Earth.

1527
02:21:40,430 --> 02:21:43,340
难道这还是不在乎？
Does that not show you that I care?

1528
02:21:46,540 --> 02:21:49,480
这里我的火星
My red world here, now...

1529
02:21:50,480 --> 02:21:53,380
如今比你的地球对我来说意义更加重大
...means more to me than your blue one.

1530
02:21:54,150 --> 02:21:55,880
好好看着
Let me show you.

1531
02:22:14,000 --> 02:22:16,940
轰炸机已经准备好了,长官
KlSSlNGER:
Bombers are fueled and ready, sir.

1532
02:22:26,280 --> 02:22:28,510
是时候了,先生们
It's time, gentlemen.

1533
02:22:30,620 --> 02:22:33,020
把战备等级提高到1级
Take us to DEFCON one.

1534
02:22:40,290 --> 02:22:43,390
不要在五角大楼,也不要在办公室里
RORSCHACH:
Not in penthouse. Not in office.

1535
02:22:43,560 --> 02:22:46,470
黑夜在这一时刻
What nocturnal proclivities
entice a man with everything...

1536
02:22:46,630 --> 02:22:48,400
