I cannot imagine
a more dangerous opponent.

1583
02:26:38,200 --> 02:26:41,630
常常开玩笑说他快的能追上子弹
Used to joke he was fast enough
to catch a bullet.

1584
02:26:41,800 --> 02:26:44,700
雪地里,他能干掉我们俩
He could kill us both alone in the snow.

1585
02:26:44,870 --> 02:26:48,570
这也是我们即将要去的地方:南极
That's where we're going now:
Antarctica.

1586
02:26:48,740 --> 02:26:51,510
不管看到日记的时候我是死是活
Whether I'm alive or dead
upon this reading...

1587
02:26:51,680 --> 02:26:55,940
我希望世界能幸存到你们看到日记的这一天
...I hope the world survives long enough
for this journal to reach you.

1588
02:26:56,120 --> 02:26:58,680
我一生从不妥协
I live my life free of compromise...

1589
02:26:58,850 --> 02:27:02,790
我涉足黑暗,无怨无悔
...and step into the shadow
without complaint or regret.

1590
02:27:03,420 --> 02:27:06,420
罗夏,11月1日
Rorschach, November 1st.

1591
02:27:06,590 --> 02:27:10,120
你就不能干脆告诉我最后是什么吗
