At some point, yes.

1595
02:27:21,440 --> 02:27:24,380
那里的街,满是死亡
The streets are filled with death.

1596
02:27:24,540 --> 02:27:26,600
乔,求你了
Jon, please.

1597
02:27:26,780 --> 02:27:31,340
你必须得阻止这些,否则大家都得死
You have to stop this. Everyone will die.

1598
02:27:31,520 --> 02:27:35,850
并且宇宙是不会注意到的
And the universe will not even notice.

1599
02:27:38,290 --> 02:27:42,520
在我看来,生命的存在
In my opinion, the existence of life...

1600
02:27:43,400 --> 02:27:46,390
只是一种被高估的现象
...is a highly overrated phenomenon.

1601
02:27:48,300 --> 02:27:50,600
看看你的周围
Just look around you.

1602
02:27:53,340 --> 02:27:57,670
没有这么多的微生物,火星依然完好无损
Mars gets along perfectly well
without so much as a microorganism.

1603
02:27:58,310 --> 02:28:02,870
这是个不断变化的地质图形
Here, it's a constantly changing
topographical map...

1604
02:28:03,050 --> 02:28:08,990
不断变幻着,激起1万年宽的涟漪
...flowing and shifting around the pole
in ripples 1 0,000 years wide.

1605
02:28:09,820 --> 02:28:11,310
告诉我
So tell me...

1606
02:28:11,490 --> 02:28:15,860
这些怎么会被仅仅一条石油管道所改变？
...how would all of this be greatly improved
by an oil pipeline?

1607
02:28:16,330 --> 02:28:18,320
