So it's too much to ask for a miracle?

1609
02:28:27,140 --> 02:28:29,270
奇迹就是无意义的东西
Miracles, by their definition,
are meaningless.

1610
02:28:29,440 --> 02:28:30,930
天啊,乔
Oh, God, Jon!

1611
02:28:31,110 --> 02:28:36,170
只有能发生的才可能发生
别再说下去了
-Only what can happen does happen.
-Just stop your bullshit.

1612
02:28:37,250 --> 02:28:39,780
赶紧让这东西着陆
Land this thing. Now.

1613
02:28:39,950 --> 02:28:42,510
遵命
JON:
As you wish.

1614
02:28:48,130 --> 02:28:49,190
你知道吗？
LAURlE:
You know what?

1615
02:28:49,360 --> 02:28:52,060
把我送回地球,让我和丹,还有我妈一起受煎熬好了
You can send me back to Earth
to fry with Dan and my mom...

1616
02:28:52,230 --> 02:28:54,600
还和其他所有不值一文的人类
...and all the other worthless humans.

1617
02:28:54,770 --> 02:28:58,200
不过你还是错了,你说了这最后会以我的眼泪结束
But know that you were wrong.
You said this ended with me in tears...

1618
02:28:58,370 --> 02:29:02,540
看看,没有眼泪,也许你什么都错了
...and look: nothing.
Maybe you were wrong about everything.

1619
02:29:02,710 --> 02:29:07,980
你抱怨我从不以生命的视角来看待生命
You complain that I refuse to see life
on life's terms...

1620
02:29:08,720 --> 02:29:12,480
但你从来不从我的视角去认知事情
...yet you continuously refuse
to see things from my perspective.

1621
02:29:12,650 --> 02:29:17,060
你封锁一切使你感到惧怕的东西
我不怕
-You shut out what you're afraid of.
-I'm not afraid.

1622
02:29:17,220 --> 02:29:22,250
你想我按你的视角认知世界？
那做给我看看,按你方法做
You want me to see things your way?
Go ahead, show me. Do that thing you do.

1623
02:29:29,400 --> 02:29:34,500
魔术,梦想,这都是我以前拥有的
我曾是个英雄,真混蛋
Magic. Dreams. That is what I had before.
I was a hero, goddamn it!

1624
02:29:34,670 --> 02:29:37,730
你变老了并不是我的错
你又有什么好抱怨的呢？
It's not my fault you got old.
What do you have to complain about?

1625
02:29:37,910 --> 02:29:40,040
我养育你还有你的孩子
I put food on the table
for you and your child.

1626
02:29:40,210 --> 02:29:43,010
你怎么不去找艾迪？或许他能给你提供更好的生活
Call your friend Eddie.
Maybe he can give you a better life.

1627
02:29:43,750 --> 02:29:46,450
就连肮脏的过去
Even the grimy parts of it...

1628
02:29:46,820 --> 02:29:49,050
也变得越来越清晰
...keep on getting brighter.

1629
02:29:49,390 --> 02:29:52,980
你妈妈,她一直以来可都是选美冠军哦
You know, your mom, she was one
of the all-time champion beauties.

1630
02:29:53,160 --> 02:29:57,600
你和她眼镜长的一样,你有…
别碰她
-You got her eyes, you know. You got--
-Take your hands off her.

1631
02:29:57,760 --> 02:29:59,890
嘿,美人,好久不见了
EDDlE:
Hey, doll. Long time no see.

1632
02:30:00,070 --> 02:30:02,830
我不这样认为,艾迪,上车
Not long enough in my book, Eddie.
Get in the car.

1633
02:30:03,340 --> 02:30:05,200
