Now.

1634
02:30:06,170 --> 02:30:08,160
你就没有点道德底线吗
Are there no depths you won't sink to?

1635
02:30:08,340 --> 02:30:12,180
神啊,难道跟…
Jesus Christ, Sally.
Can't a guy talk to his...

1636
