...you know, old friend's daughter?

1637
02:30:16,880 --> 02:30:18,210
开车
Drive.

1638
02:30:24,220 --> 02:30:27,020
当时是个错误,就那一次
SALLY:
It was a mistake. One time.

1639
02:30:27,330 --> 02:30:30,490
