喜剧演员
The Comedian...

1646
02:30:54,420 --> 02:30:56,510
是你的父亲
...was your father.

1647
02:30:57,990 --> 02:30:59,690
不
No.

1648
02:31:03,000 --> 02:31:08,700
不,不
No! No! No!

1649
02:31:41,300 --> 02:31:43,290
我的生命
My life is just...

1650
02:31:43,970 --> 02:31:46,100
简直就是个天大的玩笑
...one big joke.

1651
02:31:46,270 --> 02:31:48,830
我不这样想
I don't think your life is a joke.

1652
02:31:50,480 --> 02:31:52,470
是啊,呃
Yeah, well...

1653
02:31:54,310 --> 02:31:58,480
